{"tid":2233203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登︰若特朗普仍帶有病毒就不應該辯論","createTime":"2020-10-07T03:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:44:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"73c3d1922c93e98bbdadcb1133eeeae21148caeb","tid":2233203,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"爭取連任的美國總統特朗普，與民主黨總統候選人拜登的第二場總統大選辯論，預定10月15日在邁阿密舉行。特朗普在twitter貼文，說期待辯論舉行，認為將會很精彩。拜登就表示，如果屆時特朗普仍帶有新型冠狀病毒，他和特朗普就不應該辯論。<br />\n<br />\n拜登說，他期待能夠與特朗普辯論，但強調雙方必須遵循非常嚴格的準則，他不知道特朗普從軍方醫療中心返回白宮後的情況，但認為如果對方仍帶有病毒，就不應該進行辯論。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的競選團隊表示，拜登在當地星期二的病毒檢測結果呈陰性。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553395-20201007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553395-20201007.htm&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=97fbb3a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553395-20201007.htm&h=5af7c84f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553395-20201007.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b6527b816d91d8be5d600131f3bdfe6a437d46c0","tid":2233203,"uid":4672,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"拜登：你唔好過黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16af9d660dd03972473590ecd550342ae65eefd8","tid":2233203,"uid":7369,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"隔開d咪得囉, 咁撚驚JM9"},{"pid":"f8fb2e665882fc44b4f2e89f0c2a740b18f15099","tid":2233203,"uid":77196,"like":111,"dislike":0,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T03:33:14.000Z","msg":"屌你咁咪一人一間房黎辯論囉，而家科技咁撚發達 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc072b020313eeb985ab8ba60a942c372dab3d87","tid":2233203,"ui